With this book you will learn how to make your first shelter in Minecraft. 
Hi my name is Pranav and this is Arhan we work together. We are going to teach you how to teach you how to make a beginners
shelter in Minecraft.To get started you will need a tablet or a phone. This guide is only for those devices so if you have 
something else you are unlucky. Go onto the minecraft app and pressplay (remember this is only fore tablet)once you have done
that there will be a button apear onthe screen that says create new
tap on that and another botton will apear that says create new world tap on that and a list of things will come up at the top 
it says my world tap on it and it  will allow you to change your name of the world.once you have changed your world it is 
time to press create world located on the left.
